description": "时间窗口，如 7d, 24h, 30m"\n        },\n        "filter": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "description": "过滤条件，SQL WHERE 子句风格"\n        },\n        "aggregation": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "enum": ["COUNT", "SUM", "AVG", "MAX", "MIN", "STDDEV", "COUNT_DISTINCT", "RATIO", "FREQUENCY"],\n          "description": "聚合函数"\n        },\n        "transformation": {\n          "type": "string",\n          "enum": ["RAW", "LOG", "WOE", "BIN", "STANDARDIZE", "MINMAX", "QUANTILE_BIN"],\n          "description": "变换方法"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    "business_logic": {\n      "type": "string",\n      "minLength": 1,\n      "description": "业务含义说明"\n    },\n    "compliance_tags": {\n      "type": "array",\n      "items": {"type": "string"},\n      "minItems": 1,\n      "description": "合规标签列表"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n## 当前搜索方向\nCURRENT_DIRECTION: account_behavior\n聚焦账户行为模式，如表: account_login_log, user_profile。常用字段: login_time, login_ip, register_days, kyc_level\n\n## 当前生成策略\n- TEMPLATE_FAMILY: cross_feature\n- TRANSFORM_STRATEGY: quantile_bin\n构造两个业务字段的交叉或归一化组合。\n按分位数分箱提高鲁棒性。\n\n## 历史优秀因子\n暂无可复用优秀因子。\n\n## 历史反馈\n- [FEAT_USER_DEVICE_RISK_GEO_CHANGE_COUNT_30D_03] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: time_window | 建议: 建议缩短时间窗口以提高时效性\n- [FEAT_TRANSACTION_PATTERN_RATIO_ONLINE_CHANNEL_24H_LOG_01] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: transformation | 建议: 建议使用 WOE 或 LOG 变换提高区分度\n- [FEAT_TRANSACTION_PATTERN_RATIO_LARGE_AMOUNT_24H_LOG_03] IV=0.000000, KS=0.0000, 区分度不足 | 修正轴: filter_condition | 建议: 建议增加有效样本过滤条件\n\n## 防泄漏规则\n- 时间窗口不超过 365 天\n- 禁止使用 t+1, tomorrow, future 等未来数据关键词\n- 禁止在 filter 中使用标签字段（如 label, target）\n\n请生成 3 个特征定义，以 JSON 格式返回：{"features": [...]}'}], 'model': 'deepseek-v4-pro', 'max_tokens': 2048, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.7}}"}
